Update the Send Relationship in the Activated Data Extension

Cumulus updates the send relationship in the activated data extension.

In Marketing Cloud Engagement, navigate to Audience Builder.
From the dropdown, select Contact Builder.
Click the Data Extensions tab.
Open the Shared Items folder.
Open the Shared Data Extensions folder, and then select the Data Cloud Segments folder.
Locate the Omnichannel Credit Limit Alert data extension, and click into it.
In the Type section on the left side, click Edit.
Update the default send relationship set by Data Cloud. Relate MobilePush Key to Subscriber Key.
